    {
      "text": "Wayne Gretzky's 3D Hockey is a 1996 ice hockey video game developed and published by Atari Games for arcades. A port for the Nintendo 64 was released a month after the arcade version, making it the first-ever four-player game for the Nintendo 64. The game was followed by Wayne Gretzky's 3D Hockey '98 in 1997.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    },
    {
      "text": "The NHLPA and NHL Present: Wayne Gretzky's 3D Hockey est un jeu vidéo de hockey sur glace sorti en 1996 sur arcade, Nintendo 64 et PlayStation. Le jeu a été développé par Williams Entertainment et édité par Midway Games.",
      "lang": "fr",
      "source": "wikipedia_fr"
    }
